{"tid":2290651,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"又係洗黑錢？ - 曾志豪","createTime":"2020-11-18T07:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T07:11:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2d081191019d40f993de2cdfa89730605efba854","tid":2290651,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:11:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201118/AZW7HWSMP5H7DCCIZNABXSOV4Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201118%2FAZW7HWSMP5H7DCCIZNABXSOV4Y%2F&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1cLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=0c98f8bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201118%2FAZW7HWSMP5H7DCCIZNABXSOV4Y%2F&h=2d8cd945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201118/AZW7HWSMP5H7DCCIZNABXSOV4Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n又係洗黑錢？ - 曾志豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2CBFwoM6XujUD8F6j1yqKBRPmO4=/1279x715/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/65WRPZVBN5GOPNZ4RTRXDV753E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2CBFwoM6XujUD8F6j1yqKBRPmO4%3D%2F1279x715%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F65WRPZVBN5GOPNZ4RTRXDV753E.png&h=5e83d058&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《蘋果日報》截圖<br />\n<br />\n「阿姐，今日嘅籌款活動，希望大家參與，多多支持。」「無錯啊志蟻，希望捐款，多多益善，少少無拘&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「阿姐，唔講得多多益善，會犯法㗎﹗」「唔係啩，唔係多多益善，唔通叫大家唔好捐咁多啊？」<br />\n<br />\n「阿姐，如果大家捐太多，多過我哋今晚嘅善款目標，就會&hellip;&hellip;犯法，話我哋洗黑錢㗎啦﹗」「唔係啩﹗捐多咗錢就變咗洗黑錢？咁如果遊行人數多過預期，係咪會變咗非法集結㗎？」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。「志蟻啊，洗黑錢仲有一個條例，就係要知道善款來源係咪清白，我哋有無辦法知道啲人捐嘅錢，嚟自邊度㗎？」<br />\n<br />\n「阿姐啊，錢就冇樣睇，但啱啱有人捐咗樣物品，我就建議唔好收。」「點解？」<br />\n<br />\n「驚係賊贓。」「咩嚟㗎？」<br />\n<br />\n「鮑魚。」"}]}